---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
    title="Story & Lore - Bloom | The IEZ Cascade and Seven Factions" 
    description="Discover the rich lore of Bloom: the IEZ Cascade that fractured reality, Harvester alien technology, and seven factions fighting for survival in the quarantined city of 2161."
    keywords="Bloom story, IEZ Cascade, Harvester aliens, faction lore, quarantined city, Terminal Grounds lore, science fiction story, extraction FPS lore"
    ogImage="/assets/images/renders/hero-iez.png"
    type="article">
    
    <main class="story-page">
        <section class="hero-story quantum-grid py-24 relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="container relative z-10">
                <div class="story-header text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                    <h1 class="holographic-text text-6xl md:text-8xl font-display font-black mb-6">The World of Bloom</h1>
                    <p class="story-subtitle text-xl md:text-2xl text-text-secondary max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed mb-8">Six months after the IEZ Cascade, survival depends on more than just skill</p>
                    <div class="timeline-marker glass-morphism-advanced inline-flex items-center gap-4 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl">
                        <span class="year text-4xl font-display font-black text-primary">2161</span>
                        <div class="w-px h-8 bg-border"></div>
                        <span class="event text-text-muted uppercase tracking-wider">Post-Cascade Era</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="story-overview py-20">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="story-grid grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
                    <div class="story-content glass-morphism-advanced p-8">
                        <h2 class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-primary mb-6">The Cascade Event</h2>
                        <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">In 2161, the world changed forever. The <strong class="text-accent-cyan">IEZ Cascade</strong> created a 200-kilometer radius interdiction zone—a quarantined city-zone now known as <strong class="text-primary">Bloom</strong>. What was once civilization became a contested wasteland, reshaped by alien technology and the remnants of the mysterious <strong class="text-secondary">Harvesters</strong>.</p>
                        
                        <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">The Harvesters, absent alien extractors, left behind wreckage that defies understanding: <strong class="text-accent-cyan">Skimmer-class</strong> survey arrays, weaponized <strong class="text-secondary">Harrower-class</strong> systems, and reality-bending <strong class="text-accent-purple">Monolith-class</strong> field manipulators. These artifacts don't just power technology—they reshape the very nature of reality within Bloom.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="story-visual">
                        <div class="cascade-diagram relative w-80 h-80 mx-auto">
                            <div class="cascade-center absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-16 h-16 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-bg-primary font-bold text-sm animate-pulse">IEZ Core</div>
                            <div class="cascade-ring ring-1 absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-32 h-32 border-2 border-secondary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-secondary text-xs font-semibold">Inner Quarantine</div>
                            <div class="cascade-ring ring-2 absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-48 h-48 border-2 border-accent-cyan/50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-accent-cyan text-xs font-semibold">Contested Zone</div>
                            <div class="cascade-ring ring-3 absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-64 h-64 border border-border/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-text-muted text-xs">200km Perimeter</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="regions-section py-20 bg-bg-secondary/30">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="holographic-text text-4xl font-display font-bold text-center mb-16">Key Regions</h2>
                <div class="regions-grid grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                    <div class="region-card interactive-card glass-morphism-advanced p-6 hover:shadow-glow">
                        <div class="region-header flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-primary">The Dead Sky (IEZ)</h3>
                            <span class="danger-level high bg-red-500/20 text-red-400 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">High Risk</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">The epicenter of the Cascade. A 200km radius where reality itself became unstable. Few who enter return unchanged, but the artifacts found here are beyond measure.</p>
                        <div class="region-details flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                            <span class="detail-tag bg-accent-purple/20 text-accent-purple px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">Monolith Phenomena</span>
                            <span class="detail-tag bg-secondary/20 text-secondary px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">Reality Distortion</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="region-card interactive-card glass-morphism-advanced p-6 hover:shadow-glow">
                        <div class="region-header flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-primary">Machine Grave</h3>
                            <span class="danger-level medium bg-yellow-500/20 text-yellow-400 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">Contested</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">Semi-autonomous factories that still produce. Controlled jointly by Corporate Hegemony and Archive Keepers, these industrial complexes are vital to post-Cascade survival.</p>
                        <div class="region-details flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                            <span class="detail-tag bg-accent-cyan/20 text-accent-cyan px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">Industrial</span>
                            <span class="detail-tag bg-primary/20 text-primary px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">Factory Control</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="region-card interactive-card glass-morphism-advanced p-6 hover:shadow-glow">
                        <div class="region-header flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-primary">Metro System</h3>
                            <span class="danger-level low bg-green-500/20 text-green-400 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">Variable</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">Underground transit networks that still function. Faction control shifts daily. The safest routes for extraction—if you know who controls them.</p>
                        <div class="region-details flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                            <span class="detail-tag bg-secondary/20 text-secondary px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">Transit Network</span>
                            <span class="detail-tag bg-accent-purple/20 text-accent-purple px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">Dynamic Control</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="region-card interactive-card glass-morphism-advanced p-6 hover:shadow-glow">
                        <div class="region-header flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-primary">Tech Wastes</h3>
                            <span class="danger-level medium bg-orange-500/20 text-orange-400 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">Scavenger Territory</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">Post-industrial wasteland where technology goes to die—and be reborn. Iron Scavengers rule here, salvaging Harvester technology for those who can pay.</p>
                        <div class="region-details flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                            <span class="detail-tag bg-secondary/20 text-secondary px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">Salvage Zone</span>
                            <span class="detail-tag bg-accent-cyan/20 text-accent-cyan px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">Artifact Trade</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="artifacts-section py-20">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="holographic-text text-4xl font-display font-bold text-center mb-6">Harvester Artifacts</h2>
                <p class="section-intro text-xl text-text-secondary text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16 leading-relaxed">The absent Harvesters left behind technology that defies human understanding. Each class represents different levels of power—and danger.</p>
                
                <div class="artifacts-hierarchy grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                    <div class="artifact-tier field interactive-card glass-morphism-advanced p-8 text-center hover:shadow-glow">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-primary mb-4">Field-Class</h3>
                        <div class="artifact-icon text-6xl text-primary mb-6">◇</div>
                        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">Basic Harvester technology. Powers weapons, shields, and basic equipment. Relatively stable, widely traded.</p>
                        <div class="artifact-examples flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-center">
                            <span class="bg-primary/20 text-primary px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">Energy Cells</span>
                            <span class="bg-primary/20 text-primary px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">Shield Modules</span>
                            <span class="bg-primary/20 text-primary px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">Power Cores</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="artifact-tier splice interactive-card glass-morphism-advanced p-8 text-center hover:shadow-glow">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-secondary mb-4">Splice-Class</h3>
                        <div class="artifact-icon text-6xl text-secondary mb-6">◈</div>
                        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">Intermediate technology that interfaces with human systems. Unpredictable side effects. High reward, high risk.</p>
                        <div class="artifact-examples flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-center">
                            <span class="bg-secondary/20 text-secondary px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">Neural Interfaces</span>
                            <span class="bg-secondary/20 text-secondary px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">Reality Anchors</span>
                            <span class="bg-secondary/20 text-secondary px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">Temporal Buffers</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="artifact-tier monolith interactive-card glass-morphism-advanced p-8 text-center hover:shadow-glow">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-accent-purple mb-4">Monolith-Class</h3>
                        <div class="artifact-icon text-6xl text-accent-purple mb-6 animate-pulse">◆</div>
                        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">Reality-altering technology. Changes the fundamental rules of an area. Priceless, extremely dangerous.</p>
                        <div class="artifact-examples flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-center">
                            <span class="bg-accent-purple/20 text-accent-purple px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">Cascade Cores</span>
                            <span class="bg-accent-purple/20 text-accent-purple px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">Reality Engines</span>
                            <span class="bg-accent-purple/20 text-accent-purple px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">Field Manipulators</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="factions-overview">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">The Seven Factions</h2>
                <p class="section-intro">In the power vacuum left by the Cascade, seven major factions emerged. Each represents different philosophies of survival, control, and humanity's future.</p>
                
                <div class="faction-philosophy-grid">
                    <div class="philosophy-card order">
                        <h3>ORDER</h3>
                        <div class="philosophy-factions">
                            <div class="mini-faction">
                                <h4>Sky Bastion Directorate</h4>
                                <p>Military discipline preserves civilization</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mini-faction">
                                <h4>Civic Wardens</h4>
                                <p>Community defense protects the innocent</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="philosophy-card survival">
                        <h3>SURVIVAL</h3>
                        <div class="philosophy-factions">
                            <div class="mini-faction">
                                <h4>Iron Scavengers</h4>
                                <p>Adaptation through salvage and modification</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mini-faction">
                                <h4>Nomad Clans</h4>
                                <p>Freedom through perpetual movement</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="philosophy-card knowledge">
                        <h3>KNOWLEDGE</h3>
                        <div class="philosophy-factions">
                            <div class="mini-faction">
                                <h4>Archive Keepers</h4>
                                <p>Preservation of history and alien secrets</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mini-faction">
                                <h4>Corporate Hegemony</h4>
                                <p>Technological supremacy ensures progress</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="philosophy-card pragmatism">
                        <h3>PRAGMATISM</h3>
                        <div class="philosophy-factions">
                            <div class="mini-faction">
                                <h4>The Seventy-Seven</h4>
                                <p>Professional neutrality, competence as currency</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="timeline-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">Timeline of Events</h2>
                <div class="timeline">
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-date">2161 - Day Zero</div>
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <h4>The IEZ Cascade</h4>
                            <p>Reality fractures across a 200km zone. Harvesters vanish. Physics breaks. The quarantine begins.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-date">2161 - Week One</div>
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <h4>First Extractions</h4>
                            <p>Survivors discover Harvester artifacts. Field-class technology becomes the new currency of survival.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-date">2161 - Month One</div>
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <h4>Faction Emergence</h4>
                            <p>Seven primary factions crystallize from the chaos. Territories are claimed. The first wars begin.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-date">2161 - Month Three</div>
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <h4>The Arbitration Accords</h4>
                            <p>Factions establish rules for extraction and conflict. The reputation economy emerges.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="timeline-item current">
                        <div class="timeline-date">2161 - Month Six (NOW)</div>
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <h4>The New Normal</h4>
                            <p>Bloom has become a functioning ecosystem of conflict and cooperation. You are part of this world.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="cta-section py-20 bg-bg-secondary/30">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="cta-grid grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                    <div class="cta-card interactive-card glass-morphism-advanced p-8 text-center hover:shadow-glow">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-primary mb-4">Learn About Factions</h3>
                        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">Dive deeper into the seven major factions, their philosophies, and territories.</p>
                        <a href="/factions" class="cyber-button inline-block px-8 py-3">Explore Factions</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="cta-card interactive-card glass-morphism-advanced p-8 text-center hover:shadow-glow">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-secondary mb-4">Discover Regions</h3>
                        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">Explore the dangerous territories of Bloom and their unique challenges.</p>
                        <a href="/regions" class="px-8 py-3 bg-transparent border-2 border-secondary/30 text-secondary font-display font-bold transition-all duration-300 hover:border-secondary hover:shadow-glow hover:bg-secondary/10 inline-block rounded">View Regions</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</BaseLayout>